\I[31]\N<Flare>Ugh... F-Flame Breaker!! Flame Breaker!! Please... come

reliable!!

both so much!!

with our own hands!! We'll seize the future!!

\I[31]\N<Flare>Kenji-sama...!! Yes... Yes!! We won't let them take our
future away!!

me...!! From Black Cute-san, Pure Dark-san, Eliza-san, 
Kenji-sama... I can feel a very warm power from everyone...!!

power...!! Now... I can do it!!
\I[31]\N<Flare>Ultimate Pure Change!!

\I[31]\N<Flare>With this... with this, we will end it!! Everyone, please
lend me your strength!!
\N<Kenji>Yeah!!
\I[31]\N<Eliza>Aye, let's finish this!!

\I[31]\N<Black Cute>Hmph!! Just this time, okay!?

\I[31]\N<Everyone>Pure Breaker!!

This is... ridiculous...!! My dark energy is being
purified...!? No, noooooo...
aaaaaahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh-----------!!
\AA[F]\M[BG900mininature_004]And so, the battle ended.

\AA[F]The power of Flare and her allies completely eradicated the
Dark General's dark energy.

\AA[F]Consequently, the monsters and soldiers rampaging around
also vanished. Hinata City once again regained its peace...

\AA[F]Black Cute and Pure Dark, with the dark energy gone, their
transformations were undone, and now they enjoy a peaceful
daily life like everyone else.
\AA[F]...Or so it should have been...

\N<Black Cute>Hey, you. You've got good taste for a guy, so I'll make you
my boyfriend. You're happy, right? Be grateful.

\N<Pure Dark>Hehehe... Too bad~ Big brother is already booked by me,
okay? Right, big brother?
\N<Flare>Ufufu, Kenji-sama, you're quite popular. I'm so envious.

\N<Black Cute>I can sense the confidence of a legal wife here... it's
annoying~!! Don't worry, it's only a matter of time before
he switches from an old lady like you to someone young and
tight like me!! When I grow up, I'll have curves in all the
right places, and it'll be amazing!!

\N<Pure Dark>Hehehe... If that's the case, then I'm currently the
youngest and tightest, and I've got curves in all the right
places, so I'm the best So, big brother, let's go on a date
after school If big brother wishes, we can do even more
amazing things...

\N<Flare>Ufufu, it seems I have such a small and adorable rival now
Hehe, I can't let my guard down.

\N<Eliza>...Ah... I don't want to be part of that... Why does he get
all the attention... I can't understand it... In this
operation too, all he did was shake his hips...
The peaceful daily life continues...

The efforts of Flare and her companions protected the future
of this city, of humanity.
One couldn't help but wish for this peace to last forever.
Harem Route End
